channel.title: How do i upload higher graphics and items into a 317 server?
channel.description: If someone has a tutorial already up please give me a link to it, if there isn't any up could you please help me with this? Recently the server that i played on (rovascape.org) has recently started to die due to the owner not giving a shit about it. I have decided that I will make my own server allowing all the people from that server to transfer to it, but i don't want it to be some lame rsps. Please help, it is greatly appreciated.
